Millie Bobby Brown https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Millie_Bobby_Brown 0 Millie Bobby Brown (born 19 February 2004) is an English actress and model. She earned worldwide fame for her role as Eleven in the Netflix science fiction horror series Stranger Things, for which she received a Primetime Emmy Award nomination for Outstanding Supporting Actress in a Drama Series at the age of 13, becoming one of the youngest Emmy Award nominees of all time. She is the youngest person ever to feature on TIME 100 list of the 100 most influential people and the youngest person to be appointed as a UNICEF Goodwill Ambassador.
